<br>
Brandy (vendor) + Ice Goblin Blood (permafrost goblins) + Essence of Winter (ice giants in everfrost mainly) + Essence of Winter = Frost Temper<br>
<br>
<br>
Also with a good brewing skill and pottery skill, make Celestial Temper.  <br>
<br>
Celestial Temper = 1 purified water + 1 blue diamond dust &lt;BREW KEG&gt;<br>
Purified Water = 1 celestial essence + 1 water + 1 water &lt;BREW KEG&gt;<br>
Blue Diamond Dust = 1 Blue diamond + 1 jar of acid &lt;KILN&gt;<br>
<br>
<br>
With a good smithing skill, you can make velium rings.<br>
<br>
1 large brick of velium + 1 file + 1 velium temper (thurgadin vendor) ===&gt; forge = 2 velium rings<br>
<br>
<br>
And if you have a very good smithing skill, you can infuse them.<br>
<br>
Infused velium ring = 1 velium ring + 1 celestial temper + 1 large brick of medium quality ore + smithing hammer<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
